parameters: \nc<Saki>Y-you, was it a dream? What time is it...?

\nc<Senpai>Saki, it seems you have quite a bit of leeway this term. You
didn't even show your face on evaluation day.

\nc<Senpai>Well then... Maybe I should reduce your quota a bit for the
next quarter? Of course, I mean my quota.
\nc<Saki>Eh!? Se-senpai... that's way beyond my capabilities...

\nc<Senpai>Still planning to talk back? How about this... for every
minute from now, your quota will increase by 1%?
\nc<>After that, I went to work and got scolded to death...

\TA[1]You have achieved this term's conditions. Magic power will
be collected.
\TA[1]The target for the next term is 120,000 magic power.
